file.name: testIndentazioneOpenAPI_3.0.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
    info:
      title: Test Indentazione
      description: Test Indentazione
      version: 1.0.0
      
    servers:
      - url: http://petstore.swagger.io/api
        description: Server
    
    paths:  
      /test:
        get:
          summary: sum
          description: descr
          security:
            - bearerAuth: []
          parameters:
          - name: param1
            in: query
            required: false
            description: descr1
            schema:
              type : string
          - name: param2
            in: query
            required: true
            description: descr2
            schema:
              type : string
              format: Date
          responses:
            '200':
              description: response
              
    components:
      securitySchemes:
        basicAuth:
          type: oauth2
          flows:
            clientCredentials: 
              tokenUrl: https://example
              scopes:
                scope: s1
        bearerAuth:
          type: http
          scheme: bearer
          bearerFormat: JWT
    
    security:
      - basicAuth: []
